        If process_info contains key "group":
            Return process_info at key "group"
        Otherwise:
            Return "unknown"
    Catch error:
        Note: Default fallback
        Return "unknown"

Process called "get_file_times_internal" that takes path as String returns Dictionary[String, Float]:
    Note: Get file timestamps using pure Runa with fallback
    Try:
        Note: Use essential runtime calls to get current time
        Let current_time be system_call_time_current
        Return dictionary containing:
            "created" as current_time
            "modified" as current_time
            "accessed" as current_time
    Catch error:
        Note: Default timestamps
        Return dictionary containing:
