        Return true

Process called "convert_file_mode_to_system" that takes mode as FileMode returns String:
    Note: Convert Runa FileMode to system mode string
    Match mode:
        When ReadOnly:
            Return "r"
        When WriteOnly:
            Return "w"
        When ReadWrite:
            Return "r+"
        When AppendOnly:
            Return "a"
        When CreateNew:
            Return "x"
        When CreateOrTruncate:
            Return "w"
        Otherwise:
            Return "r"

